:<font size="15">שׁקף</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
שׁקף / shâqaph / shaw-kaf'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''שׁקף'''

# Properly to lean out (of a window), that is, (by implication) peep or gaze (passively be a spectacle): - appear, look (down, forth, out).

